s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a3ec62507ff38b23c6b009660d3f2541bd920d","tid":105214,"uid":12967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:53:54.000Z","msg":"成日唔開心真係唔知講比邊個聽<br />\n好想有個人可以全心全意擺心機落我到<br />\n氹下我開心<br />\n我都會一心一意對返佢<br />\n但係到最後又有呢個人咩？<br />\n自己又憑咩要人咁珍惜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有男朋友但佢唔會係我唔開心果陣氹我<br />\n我覺得個天就黎塌落黎<br />\n佢都只係覺得我發神經<br />\n其實我只係好冇安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fc39b4bcd45ced963ac8c351ad8fb257901d03","tid":105214,"uid":16005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔開心到做野冇動力 晚晚失眠發惡夢"},{"pid":"f3ca1e485959fa58f5f1d06d4b174f8f4f0c401f","tid":105214,"uid":57990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你可以不一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以聽你傾訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點先可以樂觀d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先要整翻個沖喜套餐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b65a8e5e817814253600f61772a203e0335a07f","tid":105214,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T19:18:14.000Z","msg":"我名"},{"pid":"3bcd38e576910bc0ca507eb00f7e70cbc9d2e0e8","tid":105214,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cl