assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你諗既野一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n已經覺得唔會有呢個人出現<br />\n以前唔開心同ex講<br />\n然後佢答我：咩話 頭先睇緊野聽唔到 講多次<br />\n<br />\n無晒心機 再都唔想同人講自己唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b716b9a5b76fa283553cb05c956be570d52b00d8","tid":105214,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔開心到做野冇動力 晚晚失眠發惡夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間歇性失眠<br />\n平時好訓得"}]}